  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a diagram of a river where the river is represented by two parallel horizontal lines. The current of the water moves from left to right at a velocity labeled v sub water, equals 5 meters per second. A point labeled O is indicated near the midpoint of the lower bank of the river. A point labeled 2 is indicated on the upper bank of the river, directly across from point O. A point labeled 1 is indicated directly to the left of point 2 and some distance from it. A pair of axes indicates that the y axis is toward the top of the page, and the x axis is to the right.\" src=\"/images/2a4769873f832da51828a3c3da7c80c8.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A person in a boat wishes to cross a river from Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"O\"><math alttext=\"O\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi></math></span></span> to Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. The water has velocity <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v sub water, equals 5 meters per second\"><math alttext=\"v sub water, equals 5 meters per second\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>v</mi><mtext>water</mtext></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mtext> m</mtext><mo>/</mo><mtext>s</mtext></math></span></span> in the positive <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span>-direction relative to the river bank, and the boat has a velocity of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v sub boat, equals 10 meters per second\"><math alttext=\"v sub boat, equals 10 meters per second\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>v</mi><mtext>boat</mtext></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mtext> m</mtext><mo>/</mo><mtext>s</mtext></math></span></span> in the positive <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>y</mi></math></span></span>-direction relative to the water. Towards which point should the boat travel to reach Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> and why?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i2",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Toward Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> because the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>y</mi></math></span></span>-component of the boat’s velocity with respect to the water needs to be  equal in magnitude to the velocity of the water.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Toward Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> because the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span>-component of the boat’s velocity with respect to the water needs to be  equal in magnitude to the velocity of the water but in the opposite direction.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Toward Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> because the magnitude of the boat’s velocity with respect to the water is greater than the magnitude of the velocity of the water.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Toward Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> because the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>y</mi></math></span></span>-component of the boat’s velocity with respect to the water is not affected by the motion of the water.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
